#
## startx note (important):
## We do NOT define any alias for startx here.
## startx (the safe wrapper installed to /usr/local/bin/startx) is only ever
## meant to be run from a bare text console / login prompt, *before* any
## graphical session or .bashrc has been sourced. Aliasing it would be
## inappropriate and potentially confusing.
